---
title: Ricotta Rigatoni and Beyond Meat® Al Forno with Spinach and Mozzarella
description: Just like Nonna's pasta al forno, this rigatoni bake is overflowing with cheese and Beyond Meat®! Creamy ricotta and gooey mozzarella give this dish its rich deliciousness, while wholesome baby spinach adds a pop of bright, fresh flavour.
